CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 2, 2009

[Cite as 12/02/2009 Case Announcements, 2009-Ohio-6210.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2009-1361. State ex rel. Brown v. Strickland.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed. Motion for admission pro hac vice of Jay Edelson by Timothy S. Rankin granted.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
